---
title: Spiced Pecan Cinnamon Rolls Serves 2 | with Crispy Bacon
description: A twist on a beloved breakfast staple, these Pumpkin Spice Cinnamon Rolls are filled with all the warming flavours of fall. Soft dough is filled with a mixture of butter, brown sugar and pumpkin pie spice to create the perfect balance of sweet and spice, and finished off with a generous helping of cream cheese glaze, because what is a breakfast bun without the icing?!

Ingredients: Pizza dough (enriched wheat flour (wheat flour, niacin, reduced iron, ascorbic acid, thiamine mononitrate, riboflavin, amylase, folic acid), water, semolina, canola oil, sugar, yeast, salt, calcium propionate, sodium stearoyl-2- lactylate, calcium sulphate) (wheat) • Bacon (pork, water, salt, sugar, sodium phosphates, sodium erythorbate, sodium nitrite, spices, smoke) • Brown sugar (cane sugar, molasses) • Icing sugar (sugar, corn starch) • Pecans • Cream cheese (milk ingredients, modified milk ingredients, salt, bacterial culture, lactic acid, guar gum, carob bean gum, xanthan gum, potassium sorbate) (milk) • Ground cinnamon • Pumpkin pie spice mix (spices).
